    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, the car is flawless; the engine runs silently and powerfully, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features function perfectly. It comes with a complete, documented service history and represents a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in essentially new condition.",
