      "description": "Presented for the discerning collector, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it remains in flawless condition, both aesthetically and mechanically. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unrivaled caliber, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original showroom debut.",
